OL,3,CRage over roadworks in Stratford-upon-
OL,4,CAvon as journey times quadruple
OL,6,FHow roadworks in Stratford are causing
OL,7,Fchaos for drivers, ITV News Central
OL,8,FProduction Journalist Ellie Griffiths
OL,9,Freports
OL,11,FRoadworks in Stratford-upon-Avon have
OL,12,Fsparked a furious reaction from
OL,13,Fmotorists as people face gridlock with
OL,14,Fhour long journeys that would usually
OL,15,Ftake minutes.
OL,17,FThe 2.8km stretch of the A439 Warwick
OL,18,FRoad towards the M40 is closed for
OL,19,Ffive months.
