OL,3,CRage over roadworks in Stratford-upon-
OL,4,CAvon as journey times quadruple
OL,6,FThese works are in place from the
OL,7,Fjunction of Welcome Road to the access
OL,8,Fof Ryan Hill Park.
OL,10,FWarwickshire County Council has said
OL,11,Fthe road closure is part of vital
OL,12,Fsafety improvements aimed at enhancing
OL,13,Froad safety for both residents and
OL,14,Fvisitors.
OL,16,FBut the project has led to increased
OL,17,Ftravel times for locals, impacting
OL,18,Fdaily commutes and the operations of
OL,19,Flocal businesses.
