OL,3,CRage over roadworks in Stratford-upon-
OL,4,CAvon as journey times quadruple
OL,6,FResidents report substantial delays,
OL,7,Fwith commutes extending significantly
OL,8,Fbeyond usual times.
OL,10,FOne road user said: "It took my
OL,11,Fdaughter an hour to drive 300 yards to
OL,12,Fthe doctors."
OL,14,FAnother said: "The traffic is
OL,15,Fhorrendous, the tourists that come and
OL,16,Fvisit, what they go home thinking
OL,17,Fheaven only knows."
OL,19,FWhile a third reported that a farmer
OL,20,Fcan't get to his sheep because of the
OL,21,Froadworks.
