OL,6,FLocal businesses are also feeling the
OL,7,Feffects, with some noting a decrease
OL,8,Fin customer footfall due to the
OL,9,Ftraffic disruptions.
OL,11,FThe New Inn Hotel and Restaurant said:
OL,12,F"We have customers not coming because
OL,13,Fof the time of the journey.
OL,15,F"Delivery drivers aren't getting here
OL,16,Fon time either and because of all of
OL,17,Fthe diversions its just taking so long
OL,18,Fto deliver."
