OL,3,CRage over roadworks in Stratford-upon-
OL,4,CAvon as journey times quadruple
OL,6,FThe importance of timely and efficient
OL,7,Ftravel to and from the town is crucial
OL,8,Ffor the local economy, especially for
OL,9,Fsectors reliant on tourism.
OL,11,FWarwickshire County Council say they
OL,12,Fhave put the roadworks in for the
OL,13,Ffollowing reasons:
OL,15,FA Warwickshire County Council
OL,16,Fspokesperson, said, "The comprehensive
OL,17,Fupgrades to the A439 Warwick Road are
OL,18,Fa major step forward in achieving the
OL,19,FCounty Council's ambition to ensuring
OL,20,Fsafe roads for everyone in
OL,21,FWarwickshire.
