OL,6,F"In the last 20 years there have sadly
OL,7,Fbeen 8 fatal collisions, 26 serious
OL,8,Fcollisions and 125 other collisions on
OL,9,Fthis road and this project aims to
OL,10,Faddress residents' concerns about
OL,11,Fspeeding, dangerous parking, and the
OL,12,Fhigh collision rate on the road.
OL,14,F"The new right hand turning lane,
OL,15,Ffootpath and cycle way, improved
OL,16,Fpedestrian crossings, physical
OL,17,Fmeasures to stop dangerous parking and
OL,18,Freduced speed limit, will make this
OL,19,Fbusy route much safer and provide
OL,20,Fresidents with a stretch of greatly
OL,21,Fimproved local infrastructure.
