OL,6,F"Whilst there unfortunately will be
OL,7,Fsome unavoidable disruption, the
OL,8,FCouncil is committed to keeping this
OL,9,Fto a minimum. A one-way southbound
OL,10,Fsystem has been implemented, and
OL,11,Fcomprehensive diversion routes are in
OL,12,Fplace, which will be clearly
OL,13,Fsignposted for the duration of the
OL,14,Fworks."
